From 0d853de019e0ec2ed65a6cf76824f309ef9276a1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vasyl Saienko <vsaienko@mirantis.com>
Date: Sat, 4 Apr 2026 17:48:11 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Harden vmedia injection/ejection

When working with vmedia in redfish make sure that iso
is actually mounted/umounted via redfish polling
bofore completing mount/umount call.
